graph LR
    CodeFlare[CodeFlare Operator<br/>v1.6.0]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    CodeFlare -->|manages lifecycle<br/>CRD watch| KubeRay[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.1.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    CodeFlare -->|webhook certs<br/>auto-rotate| CertManager[cert-manager /<br/>OCP cert-controller<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    CodeFlare -.->|workload queue<br/>optional| Kueue[Kueue<br/>v0.7.0 ODH fork<br/>OPTIONAL]
    CodeFlare -.->|service mesh<br/>optional| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|platform detection<br/>DSCInitialization watch| ODHOperator[OpenDataHub Operator<br/>opendatahub-operator]
    CodeFlare -->|metrics export<br/>ServiceMonitor| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Monitoring]
    CodeFlare -->|dashboard auth<br/>OAuth validation| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Authentication]
    CodeFlare -->|external ingress<br/>Route API| OpenShiftRoutes[OpenShift Routes<br/>route.openshift.io/v1]

    %% Infrastructure
    CodeFlare -->|CRD watch<br/>resource management<br/>HTTPS/443| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>Control Plane]

    %% Integration Points (what depends on CodeFlare)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management<br/>optional| CodeFlare
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy<br/>optional| CodeFlare
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|Ray SDK client<br/>optional| CodeFlare

    %% User interactions
    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates CRs<br/>kubectl/oc| CodeFlare
    User -->|accesses<br/>browser HTTPS| RayDashboard[Ray Dashboard<br/>via OAuth Proxy]

    CodeFlare -->|creates<br/>services, ingress| RayDashboard

    %% KubeRay creates Ray clusters
    KubeRay -->|creates<br/>Ray pods| RayCluster[Ray Cluster<br/>Head + Workers]

    %% Ray accesses storage
    RayCluster -->|fetch models<br/>HTTPS/443| S3[S3 Storage<br/>External]

    %% Kueue interaction
    Kueue -.->|admits workloads<br/>Workload CR| CodeFlare

